study_title: RtcB-mediated ligation to monitor self-cleaving ribozyme activity
experiment_title: Illumina HiSeq 2500 sequencing; Library of  T4 RNL2 TKQ ligation method with tRNA blocking
sample_alias: Library of  T4 RNL2 TKQ ligation method with tRNA blocking
description: Illumina HiSeq 2500 sequencing; Library of  T4 RNL2 TKQ ligation method with tRNA blocking
sample_description: E. coli total RNA spiked with 3-twister type P5 ribozyme fragment was used for library preparation method. RNAs with 5-PPP and 5-P were removed with RppH and Xrn1 to enrich 5-OH RNAs and tRNAs with CCA ends were blocked. Adapter was ligated to 3-OH of RNAs using T4 RNA ligase 2 truncated KQ. Sequencing was performed with ~50,000-100,000 reads and 150 bp paired-end.
